    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car has been babied from day one\u2014the paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that you\u2019d swear it was brand new. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly perfect shape and ready for some fun adventures, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
