      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that defies its age. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
      "price": 44500.0,
