    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 You seriously have to see this absolute stunner in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s finally ready for a lucky new owner to take the wheel. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new ride!",
      "price": 43500.0,
