    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E92 BMW M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 delivering linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Meticulously preserved, the vehicle shows no signs of subframe fatigue and has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement with treated shells. The factory finish is flawless, highlighting the structural integrity of the carbon-fiber reinforced plastic roof. Performance is managed by a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring precise turn-in and exceptional chassis composure. This is a collector-grade example with a documented service history and a pristine undercarriage, ready for the most discerning purist.",
